node.detail_zh: 患者為 5 個月大嬰兒，過往健康良好。2 月 20 至 6 月 30 日與母親 ( 第 #1504 宗個案患者) 及胞姊 ( 第 #1503 及 #1505 宗個案患者)曾到印度，抵港後接受強制檢疫，由檢疫中心送院，沒有病徵。
node.detail_en: The patient is a 5-month-old infant with good past health. He was in India between February 20 and July 30 with his mother (patient #1504) and elder sisters (patients #1503 and #1505). Under compulsory quarantine upon arrival in Hong Kong, he was hospitalised from quarantine centre, having exhibited no symptoms.
